sentences: Marcus Rojas (born February 23, 1963) is an American tubist from New York City.
Rojas was born in New York City on February 23, 1963, and grew up in Red Hook, Brooklyn.
Rojas formed the trio Spanish Fly with Steven Bernstein and David Tronzo in 1989.
